==English==

===Adjective===
'''ugly''' ([[uglier]], [[ugliest]])

# very unattractive, repulsive.
# displeasing to the eye, or ear, or sensibilities; unsightly.
# not aesthetically pleasing.

====Synonyms====
*[[homely]]
*[[repulsive]]
*[[unattractive]]
*[[unsightly]]

====Antonyms====
*[[beautiful]] 
*[[gorgeous]]
*[[handsome]]
*[[sightly]]

====Related terms====
*[[ugly duckling]]

